5:
Wow, this is one impressive village!
The architecture's completely
different from what I'm used to
seeing back home!
9:
This could be a handy reference
when building my next town... It's as
gorgeous of a place as I imagined it
to be!
13:
Your next town, huh... Guess it's
about time for a little remodeling.
23:
Simon'll be living there too from now
on, so I HAVE to make it an even
more amazing place than before!
27:
You guys are back. Looks like we
have company.
35: Look, Stella... It's a giant fluffball!
37:
I mean, Light's a fluffball too—just a
lot smaller.
44: Huh? What's that supposed to mean?
48:
You look different from everyone
else... From Light too...
52:
I guess it just means people come in
all different types!
57:
I take it the mission went well? Wish I
could've been there.
61:
Prika's going to stay with us for a
while. Be nice to her, Nimbus.
65:
Hold on a sec... D-does that mean
you'll be my friend?!
69:
Whoa! Gimme some space, will ya?
No need to shake me either—
73:
All right already! I'll be your bestie if
that's what you want! There, happy?!
77: Hooray! I made a new friend!
85:
People from all walks of life gather
here. I have no doubt you'll make
many friends.
88:
You think so? Whatever the case, I'm
looking forward to meeting
everyone!
93:
I just remembered... I should do
something for my friends... to show
my appreciation—
98:
Hey! Do you have a place I can
cook? Can someone show me the
way?
105:
Prika cooking for us? I should've
guessed it would be potatoes...
109:
Hm, I'm not sure if that's enough for
all of us. I messed up, didn't I...
113:
It's good eatin' nonetheless. I
wouldn't worry too much about it.
118: It's okay, Prika. You did well.
126:
What would you consider to be
quality cuisine though?
129:
Grey's cooking was a lot better than
mine... It was good, but it's all I've
ever had.
133:
Why don't we try making something
together next time, Prika?
138:
There's still plenty of steamed
potatoes... Potato salad might be a
good choice.
142:
Potato sell-it? Are we going to sell
the potatoes? But... I thought we
were going to eat them.
146:
Haha, you'll see what I mean in just
a sec.
151:
For starters, can you crush and mix
these potatoes for me? I'll chop the
vegetables in the meantime.
156:
"Crush" the potatoes... I suppose
changing the shape of ingredients
lets you make different dishes. Grey
did something similar.
162:
Whoa, whoa, whoa! We have tools
for that! Let's try to keep the kitchen
in one piece!
166:
A-am I doing it wrong? Grey told me
the same thing before...
171: Oh yeah? He must've had it rough...
174:
Well, there's a first time for
everything! C'mon, I'll show you how
to mix the potatoes.
179:
Thanks! I don't have to worry about
messing up if I'm just following your
lead!
186:
It's ready, everyone! Alk and I made
potato salad!
190: Nice job. It tastes great, Prika.
199:
You really think so?

Hooray! We did it, Alk!
203: We sure did. Thanks to you, Prika.
207:
I didn't know cooking together could
be so much fun!
210: You should join us next time, Stella!
214:
Yes, maybe I will. That does sound
nice.
218:
I think we're gonna have our hands
full for a while again... Not a problem
with me though.
222:
I'm sure you have lots of stories to
tell, Nimbus. I can't wait to hear
them all!
225:
Starview Village... It's just like I
imagined!
